var book = {
	"name": "1 Timothy",
	"numChapters": 6,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>Paul, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29698A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29698A\"></sup>an apostle of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29698B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29698B\"></sup>Christ Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29698C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29698C\"></sup>according to the commandment of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29698D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29698D\"></sup>God our Savior, and of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29698E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29698E\"></sup>Christ Jesus, <i>who is</i> our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29698F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29698F\"></sup>hope,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>To <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29699G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29699G\"></sup>Timothy, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29699H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29699H\"></sup><i>my</i> true child in <i>the</i> faith: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29699I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29699I\"></sup>Grace, mercy <i>and</i> peace from God the Father and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29699J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29699J\"></sup>Christ Jesus our Lord.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>As I urged you upon my departure for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29700K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29700K\"></sup>Macedonia, remain on at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29700L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29700L\"></sup>Ephesus so that you may instruct certain men not to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29700M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29700M\"></sup>teach strange doctrines,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>nor to pay attention to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29701N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29701N\"></sup>myths and endless <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29701O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29701O\"></sup>genealogies, which give rise to mere <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29701P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29701P\"></sup>speculation rather than <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29701Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29701Q\"></sup><i>furthering</i> the administration of God which is by faith.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But the goal of our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29702R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29702R\"></sup>instruction is love <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29702S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29702S\"></sup>from a pure heart and a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29702T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29702T\"></sup>good conscience and a sincere <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29702U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29702U\"></sup>faith.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For some men, straying from these things, have turned aside to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29703V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29703V\"></sup>fruitless discussion,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29704W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29704W\"></sup>wanting to be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29704X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29704X\"></sup>teachers of the Law, even though they do not understand either what they are saying or the matters about which they make confident assertions.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But we know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29705Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29705Y\"></sup>the Law is good, if one uses it lawfully,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>realizing the fact that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29706Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29706Z\"></sup>law is not made for a righteous person, but for those who are lawless and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29706AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29706AA\"></sup>rebellious, for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29706AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29706AB\"></sup>ungodly and sinners, for the unholy and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29706AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29706AC\"></sup>profane, for those who kill their fathers or mothers, for murderers",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29707AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29707AD\"></sup>immoral men and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29707AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29707AE\"></sup>homosexuals and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29707AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29707AF\"></sup>kidnappers and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29707AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29707AG\"></sup>liars and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29707AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29707AH\"></sup>perjurers, and whatever else is contrary to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29707AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29707AI\"></sup>sound teaching,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>according to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29708AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29708AJ\"></sup>the glorious gospel of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29708AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29708AK\"></sup>the blessed God, with which I have been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29708AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29708AL\"></sup>entrusted.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I thank <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29709AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29709AM\"></sup>Christ Jesus our Lord, who has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29709AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29709AN\"></sup>strengthened me, because He considered me faithful, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29709AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29709AO\"></sup>putting me into service,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>even though I was formerly a blasphemer and a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29710AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29710AP\"></sup>persecutor and a violent aggressor. Yet I was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29710AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29710AQ\"></sup>shown mercy because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29710AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29710AR\"></sup>I acted ignorantly in unbelief;",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29711AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29711AS\"></sup>grace of our Lord was more than abundant, with the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29711AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29711AT\"></sup>faith and love which are <i>found</i> in Christ Jesus.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29712AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29712AU\"></sup>It is a trustworthy statement, deserving full acceptance, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29712AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29712AV\"></sup>Christ Jesus came into the world to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29712AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29712AW\"></sup>save sinners, among whom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29712AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29712AX\"></sup>I am foremost <i>of all</i>.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Yet for this reason I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29713AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29713AY\"></sup>found mercy, so that in me as the foremost, Jesus Christ might <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29713AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29713AZ\"></sup>demonstrate His perfect patience as an example for those who would believe in Him for eternal life.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Now to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29714BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29714BA\"></sup>King eternal, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29714BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29714BB\"></sup>immortal, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29714BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29714BC\"></sup>invisible, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29714BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29714BD\"></sup>only God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29714BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29714BE\"></sup><i>be</i> honor and glory forever and ever. Amen.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>This <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29715BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29715BF\"></sup>command I entrust to you, Timothy, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29715BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29715BG\"></sup><i>my</i> son, in accordance with the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29715BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29715BH\"></sup>prophecies previously made concerning you, that by them you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29715BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29715BI\"></sup>fight the good fight,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>keeping <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29716BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29716BJ\"></sup>faith and a good conscience, which some have rejected and suffered shipwreck in regard to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29716BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29716BK\"></sup>their faith.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Among these are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29717BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29717BL\"></sup>Hymenaeus and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29717BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29717BM\"></sup>Alexander, whom I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29717BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29717BN\"></sup>handed over to Satan, so that they will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29717BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29717BO\"></sup>taught not to blaspheme."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>First of all, then, I urge that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29718A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29718A\"></sup>entreaties <i>and</i> prayers, petitions <i>and</i> thanksgivings, be made on behalf of all men,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29719B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29719B\"></sup>for kings and all who are in authority, so that we may lead a tranquil and quiet life in all godliness and dignity.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>This is good and acceptable in the sight of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29720C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29720C\"></sup>God our Savior,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29721D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29721D\"></sup>who desires all men to be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29721E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29721E\"></sup>saved and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29721F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29721F\"></sup>come to the knowledge of the truth.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For there is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29722G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29722G\"></sup>one God, <i>and</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29722H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29722H\"></sup>one mediator also between God and men, <i>the</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29722I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29722I\"></sup>man Christ Jesus,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29723J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29723J\"></sup>gave Himself as a ransom for all, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29723K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29723K\"></sup>testimony <i>given</i> at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29723L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29723L\"></sup>the proper time.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29724M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29724M\"></sup>For this I was appointed a preacher and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29724N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29724N\"></sup>an apostle (<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29724O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29724O\"></sup>I am telling the truth, I am not lying) as a teacher of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29724P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29724P\"></sup>the Gentiles in faith and truth.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29725Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29725Q\"></sup>I want the men <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29725R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29725R\"></sup>in every place to pray, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29725S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29725S\"></sup>lifting up <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29725T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29725T\"></sup>holy hands, without wrath and dissension.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Likewise, <i>I want</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29726U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29726U\"></sup>women to adorn themselves with proper clothing, modestly and discreetly, not with braided hair and gold or pearls or costly garments,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>but rather by means of good works, as is proper for women making a claim to godliness.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29728V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29728V\"></sup>A woman must quietly receive instruction with entire submissiveness.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29729W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29729W\"></sup>But I do not allow a woman to teach or exercise authority over a man, but to remain quiet.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29730X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29730X\"></sup>For it was Adam who was first created, <i>and</i> then Eve.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And <i>it was</i> not Adam <i>who</i> was deceived, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29731Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29731Y\"></sup>the woman being deceived, fell into transgression.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But <i>women</i> will be preserved through the bearing of children if they continue in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29732Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29732Z\"></sup>faith and love and sanctity with self-restraint."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29733A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29733A\"></sup>It is a trustworthy statement: if any man aspires to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29733B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29733B\"></sup>office of overseer, it is a fine work he desires <i>to do</i>.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29734C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29734C\"></sup>An overseer, then, must be above reproach, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29734D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29734D\"></sup>the husband of one wife, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29734E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29734E\"></sup>temperate, prudent, respectable, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29734F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29734F\"></sup>hospitable, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29734G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29734G\"></sup>able to teach,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29735H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29735H\"></sup>not addicted to wine or pugnacious, but gentle, peaceable, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29735I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29735I\"></sup>free from the love of money.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><i>He must be</i> one who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29736J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29736J\"></sup>manages his own household well, keeping his children under control with all dignity",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>(but if a man does not know how to manage his own household, how will he take care of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29737K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29737K\"></sup>the church of God?),",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><i>and</i> not a new convert, so that he will not become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29738L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29738L\"></sup>conceited and fall into the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29738M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29738M\"></sup>condemnation incurred by the devil.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And he must <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29739N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29739N\"></sup>have a good reputation with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29739O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29739O\"></sup>those outside <i>the church</i>, so that he will not fall into reproach and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29739P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29739P\"></sup>the snare of the devil.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29740Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29740Q\"></sup>Deacons likewise <i>must be</i> men of dignity, not double-tongued, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29740R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29740R\"></sup>or addicted to much wine <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29740S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29740S\"></sup>or fond of sordid gain,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29741T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29741T\"></sup><i>but</i> holding to the mystery of the faith with a clear conscience.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29742U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29742U\"></sup>These men must also first be tested; then let them serve as deacons if they are beyond reproach.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Women <i>must</i> likewise <i>be</i> dignified, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29743V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29743V\"></sup>not malicious gossips, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29743W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29743W\"></sup>temperate, faithful in all things.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29744X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29744X\"></sup>Deacons must be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29744Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29744Y\"></sup>husbands of <i>only</i> one wife, <i>and</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29744Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29744Z\"></sup>good managers of <i>their</i> children and their own households.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For those who have served well as deacons <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29745AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29745AA\"></sup>obtain for themselves a high standing and great confidence in the faith that is in Christ Jesus.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I am writing these things to you, hoping to come to you before long;",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>but in case I am delayed, <i>I write</i> so that you will know how one ought to conduct himself in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29747AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29747AB\"></sup>the household of God, which is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29747AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29747AC\"></sup>church of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29747AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29747AD\"></sup>the living God, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29747AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29747AE\"></sup>pillar and support of the truth.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>By common confession, great is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29748AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29748AF\"></sup>the mystery of godliness:He who was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29748AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29748AG\"></sup>revealed in the flesh,Was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29748AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29748AH\"></sup>vindicated in the Spirit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29748AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29748AI\"></sup>Seen by angels,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29748AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29748AJ\"></sup>Proclaimed among the nations,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29748AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29748AK\"></sup>Believed on in the world,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29748AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29748AL\"></sup>Taken up in glory."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29749A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29749A\"></sup>the Spirit explicitly says that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29749B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29749B\"></sup>in later times some will fall away from the faith, paying attention to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29749C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29749C\"></sup>deceitful spirits and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29749D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29749D\"></sup>doctrines of demons,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>by means of the hypocrisy of liars <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29750E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29750E\"></sup>seared in their own conscience as with a branding iron,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><i>men</i> who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29751F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29751F\"></sup>forbid marriage <i>and advocate</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29751G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29751G\"></sup>abstaining from foods which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29751H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29751H\"></sup>God has created to be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29751I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29751I\"></sup>gratefully shared in by those who believe and know the truth.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29752J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29752J\"></sup>everything created by God is good, and nothing is to be rejected if it is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29752K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29752K\"></sup>received with gratitude;",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>for it is sanctified by means of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29753L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29753L\"></sup>the word of God and prayer.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>In pointing out these things to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29754M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29754M\"></sup>the brethren, you will be a good <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29754N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29754N\"></sup>servant of Christ Jesus, <i>constantly</i> nourished on the words of the faith and of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29754O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29754O\"></sup>sound doctrine which you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29754P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29754P\"></sup>have been following.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But have nothing to do with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29755Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29755Q\"></sup>worldly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29755R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29755R\"></sup>fables fit only for old women. On the other hand, discipline yourself for the purpose of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29755S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29755S\"></sup>godliness;",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29756T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29756T\"></sup>bodily discipline is only of little profit, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29756U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29756U\"></sup>godliness is profitable for all things, since it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29756V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29756V\"></sup>holds promise for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29756W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29756W\"></sup>present life and <i>also</i> for the <i>life</i> to come.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29757X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29757X\"></sup>It is a trustworthy statement deserving full acceptance.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For it is for this we labor and strive, because we have fixed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29758Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29758Y\"></sup>our hope on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29758Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29758Z\"></sup>the living God, who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29758AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29758AA\"></sup>the Savior of all men, especially of believers.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29759AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29759AB\"></sup>Prescribe and teach these things.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29760AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29760AC\"></sup>Let no one look down on your youthfulness, but <i>rather</i> in speech, conduct, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29760AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29760AD\"></sup>love, faith <i>and</i> purity, show yourself <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29760AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29760AE\"></sup>an example of those who believe.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29761AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29761AF\"></sup>Until I come, give attention to the <i>public</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29761AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29761AG\"></sup>reading <i>of Scripture</i>, to exhortation and teaching.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Do not neglect the spiritual gift within you, which was bestowed on you through <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29762AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29762AH\"></sup>prophetic utterance with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29762AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29762AI\"></sup>the laying on of hands by the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29762AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29762AJ\"></sup>presbytery.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Take pains with these things; be <i>absorbed</i> in them, so that your progress will be evident to all.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29764AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29764AK\"></sup>Pay close attention to yourself and to your teaching; persevere in these things, for as you do this you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29764AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29764AL\"></sup>ensure salvation both for yourself and for those who hear you."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29765A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29765A\"></sup>Do not sharply rebuke an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29765B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29765B\"></sup>older man, but <i>rather</i> appeal to <i>him</i> as a father, <i>to</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29765C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29765C\"></sup>the younger men as brothers,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>the older women as mothers, <i>and</i> the younger women as sisters, in all purity.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Honor widows who are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29767D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29767D\"></sup>widows indeed;",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>but if any widow has children or grandchildren, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29768E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29768E\"></sup>they must first learn to practice piety in regard to their own family and to make some return to their parents; for this is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29768F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29768F\"></sup>acceptable in the sight of God.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Now she who is a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29769G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29769G\"></sup>widow indeed and who has been left alone, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29769H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29769H\"></sup>has fixed her hope on God and continues in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29769I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29769I\"></sup>entreaties and prayers night and day.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But she who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29770J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29770J\"></sup>gives herself to wanton pleasure is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29770K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29770K\"></sup>dead even while she lives.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29771L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29771L\"></sup>Prescribe these things as well, so that they may be above reproach.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But if anyone does not provide for his own, and especially for those of his household, he has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29772M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29772M\"></sup>denied the faith and is worse than an unbeliever.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>A widow is to be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29773N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29773N\"></sup>put on the list only if she is not less than sixty years old, <i>having been</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29773O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29773O\"></sup>the wife of one man,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>having a reputation for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29774P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29774P\"></sup>good works; <i>and</i> if she has brought up children, if she has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29774Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29774Q\"></sup>shown hospitality to strangers, if she <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29774R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29774R\"></sup>has washed the saints’ feet, if she has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29774S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29774S\"></sup>assisted those in distress, <i>and</i> if she has devoted herself to every good work.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But refuse <i>to put</i> younger widows <i>on the list</i>, for when they feel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29775T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29775T\"></sup>sensual desires in disregard of Christ, they want to get married,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><i>thus</i> incurring condemnation, because they have set aside their previous pledge.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>At the same time they also learn <i>to be</i> idle, as they go around from house to house; and not merely idle, but also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29777U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29777U\"></sup>gossips and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29777V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29777V\"></sup>busybodies, talking about <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29777W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29777W\"></sup>things not proper <i>to mention</i>.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Therefore, I want younger <i>widows</i> to get <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29778X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29778X\"></sup>married, bear children, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29778Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29778Y\"></sup>keep house, <i>and</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29778Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29778Z\"></sup>give the enemy no occasion for reproach;",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>for some <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29779AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29779AA\"></sup>have already turned aside to follow <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29779AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29779AB\"></sup>Satan.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>If any woman who is a believer <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29780AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29780AC\"></sup>has <i>dependent</i> widows, she must <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29780AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29780AD\"></sup>assist them and the church must not be burdened, so that it may assist those who are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29780AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29780AE\"></sup>widows indeed.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29781AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29781AF\"></sup>The elders who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29781AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29781AG\"></sup>rule well are to be considered worthy of double honor, especially those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29781AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29781AH\"></sup>work hard at preaching and teaching.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For the Scripture says, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29782AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29782AI\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">You shall not muzzle the ox while he is threshing</span>,” and “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29782AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29782AJ\"></sup>The laborer is worthy of his wages.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Do not receive an accusation against an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29783AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29783AK\"></sup>elder except on the basis of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29783AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29783AL\"></sup>two or three witnesses.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Those who continue in sin, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29784AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29784AM\"></sup>rebuke in the presence of all, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29784AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29784AN\"></sup>so that the rest also will be fearful <i>of sinning</i>.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29785AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29785AO\"></sup>I solemnly charge you in the presence of God and of Christ Jesus and of <i>His</i> chosen angels, to maintain these <i>principles</i> without bias, doing nothing in a <i>spirit of</i> partiality.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29786AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29786AP\"></sup>Do not lay hands upon anyone <i>too</i> hastily and thereby share <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29786AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29786AQ\"></sup><i>responsibility for</i> the sins of others; keep yourself free from sin.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>No longer drink water <i>exclusively</i>, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29787AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29787AR\"></sup>use a little wine for the sake of your stomach and your frequent ailments.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>The sins of some men are quite evident, going before them to judgment; for others, their <i>sins</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29788AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29788AS\"></sup>follow after.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Likewise also, deeds that are good are quite evident, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29789AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29789AT\"></sup>those which are otherwise cannot be concealed."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29790A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29790A\"></sup>All who are under the yoke as slaves are to regard their own masters as worthy of all honor so <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29790B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29790B\"></sup>that the name of God and <i>our</i> doctrine will not be spoken against.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Those who have believers as their masters must not be disrespectful to them because they are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29791C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29791C\"></sup>brethren, but must serve them all the more, because those who partake of the benefit are believers and beloved. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29791D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29791D\"></sup>Teach and preach these <i>principles</i>.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>If anyone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29792E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29792E\"></sup>advocates a different doctrine and does not agree with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29792F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29792F\"></sup>sound words, those of our Lord Jesus Christ, and with the doctrine <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29792G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29792G\"></sup>conforming to godliness,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>he is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29793H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29793H\"></sup>conceited <i>and</i> understands nothing; but he has a morbid interest in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29793I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29793I\"></sup>controversial questions and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29793J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29793J\"></sup>disputes about words, out of which arise envy, strife, abusive language, evil suspicions,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>and constant friction between <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29794K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29794K\"></sup>men of depraved mind and deprived of the truth, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29794L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29794L\"></sup>suppose that godliness is a means of gain.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29795M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29795M\"></sup>But godliness <i>actually</i> is a means of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29795N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29795N\"></sup>great gain when accompanied by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29795O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29795O\"></sup>contentment.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29796P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29796P\"></sup>we have brought nothing into the world, so we cannot take anything out of it either.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>If we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29797Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29797Q\"></sup>have food and covering, with these we shall be content.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29798R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29798R\"></sup>But those who want to get rich fall into temptation and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29798S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29798S\"></sup>a snare and many foolish and harmful desires which plunge men into ruin and destruction.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29799T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29799T\"></sup>the love of money is a root of all sorts of evil, and some by longing for it have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29799U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29799U\"></sup>wandered away from the faith and pierced themselves with many griefs.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29800V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29800V\"></sup>flee from these things, you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29800W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29800W\"></sup>man of God, and pursue righteousness, godliness, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29800X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29800X\"></sup>faith, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29800Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29800Y\"></sup>love, perseverance <i>and</i> gentleness.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29801Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29801Z\"></sup>Fight the good fight of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29801AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29801AA\"></sup>faith; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29801AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29801AB\"></sup>take hold of the eternal life <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29801AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29801AC\"></sup>to which you were called, and you made the good <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29801AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29801AD\"></sup>confession in the presence of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29801AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29801AE\"></sup>many witnesses.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29802AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29802AF\"></sup>I charge you in the presence of God, who gives life to all things, and of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29802AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29802AG\"></sup>Christ Jesus, who testified the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29802AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29802AH\"></sup>good confession <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29802AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29802AI\"></sup>before Pontius Pilate,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>that you keep the commandment without stain or reproach until the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29803AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29803AJ\"></sup>appearing of our Lord Jesus Christ,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>which He will bring about at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29804AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29804AK\"></sup>the proper time—He who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29804AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29804AL\"></sup>the blessed and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29804AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29804AM\"></sup>only Sovereign, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29804AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29804AN\"></sup>the King of kings and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29804AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29804AO\"></sup>Lord of lords,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29805AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29805AP\"></sup>who alone possesses immortality and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29805AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29805AQ\"></sup>dwells in unapproachable light, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29805AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29805AR\"></sup>whom no man has seen or can see. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29805AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29805AS\"></sup>To Him <i>be</i> honor and eternal dominion! Amen.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Instruct those who are rich in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29806AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29806AT\"></sup>this present world <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29806AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29806AU\"></sup>not to be conceited or to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29806AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29806AV\"></sup>fix their hope on the uncertainty of riches, but on God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29806AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29806AW\"></sup>who richly supplies us with all things to enjoy.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><i>Instruct them</i> to do good, to be rich in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29807AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29807AX\"></sup>good works, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29807AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29807AY\"></sup>to be generous and ready to share,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29808AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29808AZ\"></sup>storing up for themselves the treasure of a good foundation for the future, so that they may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29808BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29808BA\"></sup>take hold of that which is life indeed.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29809BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29809BB\"></sup>Timothy, guard <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29809BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29809BC\"></sup>what has been entrusted to you, avoiding <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29809BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29809BD\"></sup>worldly <i>and</i> empty chatter <i>and</i> the opposing arguments of what is falsely called “knowledge”—",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>which some have professed and thus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29810BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29810BE\"></sup>gone astray from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29810BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29810BF\"></sup>the faith.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29810BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29810BG\"></sup>Grace be with you."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;